No. 638. Maggie Myers, Appellant, v. Andrew P. Wymore, Late Sheriff, etc., et al. April 22, 1907. Mr. James S. Easby-Smith, Mr. W. E. Fowler and Mr. R. B. Ruff for appellant. Mr. Herbert, S. Hadley for appellees.

Appeal from the District Court of the United States for the Western District'of Missouri.

Dismissed with costs, pursuant to the tenth rule.
